data.description: Stunning 2-story home in highly desirable neighborhood! Step inside and be greeted by elegant and spacious living spaces adorned with 10ft+ high vaulted ceilings, dazzling chandeliers, and convenient ceiling fans. A charming formal living/dining room perfect for hosting gatherings. Kitchen boasts oak cabinetry, tile counters, stainless steel appliances & an island. Cozy up by the fireplace in the inviting family room, and revel in the abundance of entertaining and storage space throughout. Backyard oasis meticulously landscaped with a vibrant lawn, concrete spaces/walkways, fruit trees, and fragrant rose bushes. Upgrades include new electric/energy-efficient HVAC system & water heater, upgraded toilets, showerheads &  widened driveway with parking for three vehicles. This home resides in a high demand area, offering the convenience of a 2-min walk to Smedberg MS & Sheldon HS & a quick 3-min drive to Robert J. Fite Elem. You'll appreciate the proximity to restaurants, shopping, parks, and freeways, making daily life a breeze. Located in the coveted South Sac. borderline next to Elk Grove, this opportunity is truly exceptional. Don't miss out on the chance to call this magnificent property your own!
